\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999966229641083, \"rank\": 2.465128365074445e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both sport climbing events\", \"from\": 45, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"Brooke Raboutoubecame\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 147}, {\"ngram\": \"the discipline's Olympic debut\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raboutou and 20 other women went head to head in a controversial triple-combined event, vying for a single gold medal based on an aggregate score from three different events: speed, bouldering, and lead.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raboutou\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"20 other women\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"a controversial triple-combined event\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"a single gold medal\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"an aggregate score\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"three different events\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"bouldering\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"lead\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While bouldering and lead climbing share some characteristics-a focus on strength and the technical difficulty of climbing movement-speed climbing is a sport all its own, and requires a very different skillset.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"climbing\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"some characteristics\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"the technical difficulty\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"movement-speed climbing\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"a very different skillset\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The formatreceived ample criticism.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The formatreceived ample criticism\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raboutou had a strong showing in bouldering, coming second behind Slovenian Janja Garnbret, who eventually won the gold medal.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"score\": 0.9969309238966958, \"rank\": 0.0025131210764447356, \"text\": \"Slovenian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janja Garnbret\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raboutou\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong showing\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"bouldering\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she struggled in the other two disciplines and eventually finished fifth.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other two disciplines\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Raboutou is back, and she hopes to grab a medal in sport climbing at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raboutou\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"sport climbing\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theclimbing eventsrun August 5-10.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eventsrun\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Things are different for Raboutou and the other climbers whose sights are set on the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Things\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"Raboutou\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the other climbers\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"whose sights\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For starters, the International Olympic Committee has dramatically changed the format: speed climbing a stand-alone medal event in Paris.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995485946893, \"rank\": 4.514053326507151e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"starters\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"the format\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a stand-alone medal event\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A second set of medals will be awarded based off of combined scores in the bouldering and lead competitions.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A second set\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"combined scores\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the bouldering and lead competitions\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We spoke with Raboutou about her ambitions in Paris, the atmosphere at the world's biggest stage, and what the new format means for the world's best competitive sport climbers.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995485946893, \"rank\": 4.514053326507151e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raboutou\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"her ambitions\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest stage\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"the new format\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best competitive sport climbers\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OUTSIDE: What is your opinion of the new Olympic competition format?I think it's a great change, and I do not know anyone who would argue it is not.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OUTSIDE\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"your opinion\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the new Olympic competition format?I\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"a great change\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I competed in Tokyo, it was all three disciplines combined into one.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.997071888523376, \"rank\": 0.0029366763237731485, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three disciplines\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That wasn't only grueling physically, but the way it worked out for scoring wasn't really fair.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"scoring\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was ranking-based.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I can say none of us would have chosen to compete in all three events at once.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"all three events\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The combined format did favor some competitors over others, but in general, Speed is a specialty that deserves its own medals.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The combined format\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"some competitors\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"Speed\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"a specialty\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"its own medals\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully in the future Boulder and Lead will also be separate and then there will be a Combined event as well.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.453053995040336e-21, \"text\": \"Boulder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lead\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"a Combined event\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But still, those are much more similar disciplines and require similar skills.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much more similar disciplines\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"similar skills\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of us competitors do specialize in both of those, but not all three.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"us competitors\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think it makes a lot more sense for our sport and gives the opportunity for speed climbers to go to the Olympics and have their own medals.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot more sense\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"speed climbers\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"their own medals\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people are still annoyed that Boulder and Lead are combined.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.453053995040336e-21, \"text\": \"Boulder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"Lead\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is only our second Games, so I am grateful for anything we can get.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only our second Games\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That first split is incredible, and hopefully we can gain more traction and opportunities for more medal sets in the future that will allow more specialization.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That first split\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"more traction\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"more medal sets\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"more specialization\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I honestly do like the combined approach, so I hope we can have both individual and combined in the future.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the combined approach\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just trying to take it as it comes and be grateful that we are on this big stage.\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this big stage\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What did your training look like in the lead up to Paris?I will give you the basics.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your training\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris?I\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"the basics\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I climb five days a week, usually two days on, one day off, sometimes three days on, one or two days off.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My training is planned, but it's also adaptable.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My training\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I train with a coach here who I have worked with for four years, Chris Danielson, who's a big part of my growth.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"a big part\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"my growth\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a huge mentor to me.\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge mentor\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of the training is on the wall, climbing, but I do strength training as well, weights for power and maintenance.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"strength training\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3509}, {\"ngram\": \"maintenance\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I do a lot of mental work.\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3546}, {\"ngram\": \"mental work\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mental work, like visualization or medication?Both.\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mental work\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"visualization\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"medication?Both\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meditation just for my own well-being, and then visualization-working with sports psychologists and practicing imagery tactics to use throughout training and competition.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meditation\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"my own well-being\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3653}, {\"ngram\": \"sports psychologists\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3711}, {\"ngram\": \"imagery tactics\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's both visualization of the climbs, but also different cues to help get me in the present moment, focused on myself, and in a good mental place.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both visualization\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"the climbs\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"different cues\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"the present moment\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3888}, {\"ngram\": \"a good mental place\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How does the atmosphere of the Olympics differ from that at major climbing events like the World Cup?I remember having a moment of realization at the Games because it did feel so different in some ways.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"major climbing events\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup?I\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"realization\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4093}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LikeThis is crazy.\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LikeThis\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is climbing's first Olympics, and there are only 20 of us on the mat.So I had that realization, but still, we are just climbing.\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first Olympics\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4222}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4233}, {\"ngram\": \"that realization\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the same game that we get to do every day, at all the other competitions.\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same game\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4315}, {\"ngram\": \"all the other competitions\", \"from\": 4348, \"to\": 4374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's more a perception change than an actual change, which to me is helpful.\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perception change\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4406}, {\"ngram\": \"an actual change\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like to look at it that way.\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an exciting opportunity, how big this is, but at the end of the day, nothing has changed.\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an exciting opportunity\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4539, \"to\": 4546}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4557}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are still doing what we love out there on the mats.\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mats\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not know.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would say yes and no.\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is different for sure, but a lot of that is just perception as well, and attention toward our sport, less real internal change or physical change.\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"just perception\", \"from\": 4724, \"to\": 4739}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4762}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4779}, {\"ngram\": \"less real internal change\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"physical change\", \"from\": 4810, \"to\": 4825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What draws you to competitive climbing?I love climbing just for itself, for the movement.\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 4916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something that drives me and I am impassioned by, and I find that both indoors and outdoors.\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 5017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have really fallen in love with competition for the mental growth that it takes.\", \"from\": 5018, \"to\": 5104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental growth\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learning about myself through competition, through challenges, through success, it's been really eye-opening and purposeful for me.\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 5135, \"to\": 5146}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"eye-opening\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be a high-level competitor and get to experience this world and those extremes, and have that time for myself to reflect on how I show up.\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high-level competitor\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5267}, {\"ngram\": \"this world\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5300}, {\"ngram\": \"those extremes\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5319}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have learned so much through competition climbing about my own development.\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5422}, {\"ngram\": \"my own development\", \"from\": 5438, \"to\": 5456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something I am really grateful for and love on a bigger picture perspective.\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5465, \"to\": 5474}, {\"ngram\": \"a bigger picture perspective\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Internally, I love the movement of climbing, and I love the feelings it gives me and the confidence it gives me in the way I am able to express myself.\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 5561, \"to\": 5573}, {\"ngram\": \"climbing\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"the feelings\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5610}, {\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5641}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This interview was edited for space and clarity.\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This interview\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5709}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5730}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5742}]}]}"